  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Ski Holidays were simply made for groups-<strong> NEW OFFER</strong>- up to <strong>1 in 4 go free</strong> with Inghams when you book by 18th April 2016<br /><br /><strong>Thursday 3rd March 2016, Godalming</strong>- Memories last a lifetime and there is no better way to create them than by zipping down a red ski run, sipping glühwein in the mountains or relaxing in a home-from-home chalet. So it’s time to grab your friends and head to the slopes as Inghams has some even better savings for winter 2016/17. <br /><br />On bookings made by Monday 18th April 2016 Inghams is offering <strong>increased savings</strong> on group bookings for Winter 2016/17 holidays <strong>including Christmas and New Year weeks</strong>. For example, in addition to the existing group savings (up to one in five go free) on bookings made before 18th April 2016 on groups between 8-19- an extra half a free place, groups of 20-25 one extra free place and groups of 26-39 1.5 extra free places which means up to one in four go free. Other benefits include;<br /><br />• Free lift pass for group leaders- available in most European resorts in groups of 15 or over when all members pre-book their lift pass with Inghams. <br />• Free group seating on charter flights<br />• Free travel insurance offer for group leaders<br />• Free name changes up to four weeks before departure<br />• Free lift pass delivery either on the transfer or on arrival<br />• Group dining<br />• Group ski lesson- we can arrange for you and group to ski together with dedicated lessons for groups of 10 or more. <br />• Group discounts from groups of six upwards<br />• Flexible flying from 27 UK airports<br />• Pre-bookable ski lift pass, hire and tuition for a smooth start to your ski holiday<br />• Free thinking time- we’ll put your holiday on hold giving you time to think before booking</p>
<p><br /><em>Terms and conditions apply, available on all dates except 11th and 18th February 2017 departures.</em> <br /><br /><strong>For more information about our group savings visit</strong> <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/skigroups%20">www.inghams.co.uk/skigroups </a>or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>ENDS.</strong></p>
